- `scripts/smoke_test_runner.py` - Orchestrate smoke test suite with environment config
- `scripts/metrics_collector.py` - Collect and compare metrics against baseline
- `scripts/rollback_automation.sh` - Automated rollback for multiple platforms
- `scripts/release_notes_generator.py` - Generate release notes from story documents

